programme.title: Stanley Cup Playoff: Game 1: Washington Capitals at Vegas Golden Knights
programme.sub-title: Game 1: Washington Capitals at Vegas Golden Knights
programme.desc: Washington Capitals at Vegas Golden Knights in Game 1 of the Stanley Cup Final. From T-Mobile Arena. Alex Ovechkin leads the Caps against goalie Marc-Andre Fleury and expansion Vegas, a team built by George McPhee, who was Washington GM from 1997-2014 and oversaw the franchise's only previous Cup finalist in 1998. Knights defenseman Nate Schmidt was plucked from the Caps in the expansion draft. Vegas won both regular-season meetings, 3-0 and 4-3. (cc).
